:122874,"uid":85336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>眾叛親離<br />\n呢條友係有啲問題<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢肯行本土路線，都可以睇下既</blockquote><br />\n收檔啦，條友又想食本土票，又驚得失傳統泛民票，結果兩頭唔到岸，立場左搖右擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衰燃過擺明行泛民"},{"pid":"356a5f7c9e9eeb515b8739e3057e1e96b2527889","tid":122874,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"佢將軍澳好多樁腳喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢走咗去九西班將軍澳區議員點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳啲本土組織係時候搶位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324e244f633e87c4d59091550381c15c7fb371c0","tid":122874,"uid":85336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢將軍澳好多樁腳喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢走咗去九西班將軍澳區議員點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳啲本土組織係時候搶位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢將軍澳有隻腳先又走左去幫鄭家富"},{"pid":"d023709653d893b812953e1bcff46c9dc000f200","tid":122874,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"死得仲慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db588d44dee419a02eed0ca477ba3f59d240c3b7","tid":122874,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"前屆新東選左你已經俾高登仔串到一棟都無<br />\n<br />\n依家搬左過黎九西 你咪再過黎阿唔該..."},{"pid":"e3e82b7215847b7f08ab176a78b507b22d117bf2","tid":122874,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死得仲慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會慘得過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ffc140f26c38d128e41b5345ba8a4f7ef3ccea","tid":122874,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"763e38c9bc79e0f80eb1e19f444097fc06092d88","tid":122874,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"民主黨出身既都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7802e58c163f1a52f04afbcc576b2ca38b03752b","tid":122874,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"新民主同盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我仲記得佢地超區退選個陣講撚到自己比人迫害咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己無民望就瀨屎瀨屁<br />\n<br />\n而家睇返只不過係一堆撈唔起既白鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同新思維沒有半點分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}